sequenceDiagram
    participant IC as IronClaw Worker
    participant WS as Webshell API
    participant LP as LiteLLM Proxy (:4000)
    participant AP as Anthropic API
    participant BG as BudgetGuard (AppState)
    participant SSE as SSE Broadcast
    participant Op as Operator

    Note over IC,LP: IronClaw wave dispatch — worker carrying virtual key sk-ironclaw-<build-id>
    IC->>WS: POST /api/builds {mode: autonomous, waves: [...]}
    WS->>LP: POST /v1/chat/completions {Authorization: Bearer sk-ironclaw-<build-id>}
    LP->>LP: budget_check(sk-ironclaw-...) → current=$0.48, max=$0.50 → OK
    LP->>AP: forward request
    AP-->>LP: 200 streaming response
    LP-->>WS: 200 streaming
    WS-->>IC: stream chunks

    Note over IC,LP: Next wave — budget exceeded
    IC->>WS: POST /api/builds {mode: autonomous, waves: [...]}
    WS->>LP: POST /v1/chat/completions
    LP->>LP: budget_check → current=$0.52, max=$0.50 → EXCEEDED
    LP-->>WS: 429 {"error": {"type": "budget_exceeded", "code": 429}}

    WS->>BG: set ironclaw_budget_exceeded = true
    WS->>SSE: broadcast BudgetExhausted {build_id, reason}
    SSE->>Op: SSE event → UI shows budget alert
    WS-->>IC: 429 propagated → IronClaw halts

    Note over Op,WS: Operator must explicitly override to resume
    Op->>WS: POST /api/builds/<id>/budget-override {approved: true}
    WS->>BG: clear ironclaw_budget_exceeded
    WS-->>Op: 200 OK — build may resume
